{"tid":1334096,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［有線當年今日2011］警隊教戰手冊網上任睇","createTime":"2019-07-20T03:49:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T12:58:41.000Z","uid":1723,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d466ecbe49a92b681284a7ea94b6cbec8d6033d0","tid":1334096,"uid":1723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T03:49:41.000Z","msg":"【日日有頭條】<br />\n【警隊教戰手冊網上任睇】<br />\n<br />\n警員面對突發事件要如何應變？對手持摺凳的示威者，要如何應付？<br />\n<br />\n北京有位教授，就曾經完完整整地將香港警方的教戰手冊放上網跟網民交流。<br />\n<br />\n#有線新聞 #日日有頭條 #20110720 #教戰手冊 #香港警察 #示威<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1161650170693716&amp;id=186040714921338\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1161650170693716%26id%3D186040714921338&d=JxnBaozbJlL%2F%2BfT%2BMtMvbnf7N2ZoUQ5IAXdO3fO0pAc%3D&h=beed5dfa\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1161650170693716&amp;id=186040714921338</a><br />\n<br />\n有線喺呢個時候搵番呢啲嘢出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b91d101a32298b151dcf02a257fc45f991a13cfa","tid":1334096,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T03:50:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>保障手足 指出偽警</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">極不建議自行逮捕</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但必須當場指出冒警人士</span><br />\n撲滅罪行 你我有責<br />\n<br />\n【有人冒警】面對冒警情境練習場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1332100\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1332100</a><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">有人冒警\n你扮警察\n冇委任證\n涉嫌傷人\n藏有攻擊性武器\n我地行使公民逮捕權</code></pre>"},{"pid":"be4f3fbd07b3ecbb0473556cc5ca5128a28f0daf","tid":1334096,"uid":225798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T03:51:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe538a867de04780ed672961dd8ee9a9882813b4","tid":1334096,"uid":197570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"